And thought she was doing it . 
Thought she had felt a little flutter in its chest , and was trying if it had breath at all . 
Colonel Tom thinks of what big folks the Buckner fambly has always been at home . 
And how high they had always held their heads . 
And how none of the women has ever been like this before . 
Nor no disgrace of any kind . 
And that there kid , if it is alive , is a sign of disgrace . 
And he hoped to God , he said , it wasn't alive . 
But he don't say so . 
