The long and short of it was , Colonel Tom went on to tell , that the nurse went out and got her mother . 
Which the two of them lived alone , only around the corner . 
And give the child into the keeping of her mother , who took it away then and there . 
Colonel Tom had made up his mind there wasn't going to be no bastards in the Buckner fambly . 
And now that Miss Lucy thought it was dead he would let her keep on thinking so . 
And that would be settled for good and all . 
He figgered that it wouldn't ever hurt her none if she never knowed it . 
